OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain east at first
OL,6,Fwith showers soon following from the
OL,7,Fwest, these becoming frequent for a
OL,8,Ftime in the morning.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA few early showers in the
OL,11,Fwest otherwise dry and cold with clear
OL,12,Fspells becoming cloudy towards morning
OL,13,Fwith rain in the south.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FCloudy with rain spreading
OL,16,Fnorth, this wintry on the hills. Rain
OL,17,Fwill turn to showers from late
OL,18,Fmorning. The wind strengthens in the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
