OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FThe
OL,6,Fwind will ease early Sunday, showers,
OL,7,Fwintry on the hills clear late Sunday.
OL,8,FMonday and early Tuesday will be
OL,9,Fmostly dry but showers then rain push
OL,10,Feast through Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
